    <h1>Privacy Policy and Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: May 2, 2026</p>
    <p class="intro">This page explains how Big Tuna handles data and the terms that apply when you use the Big Tuna Discord bot and website.</p>

    <div class="quickLinks">
